  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">EMCD with an electron vortex filter: Limitations and possibilities</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="c">2017-03-19</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">• The feasibility of detecting an EMCD signal with a vortex filter mask is discussed. • The dichroic signal of ferromagnetic cobalt is estimated on theoretical grounds. • It is shown that magnetic dichroism can, in principle, be detected. • A trial experiment shows that the SNR is ten times too low for EMCD detection.</subfield>
